{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3724 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3724 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3724","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"must #include <ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>windows.h&gt; to use multi-threading with events","pos":[618,679],"source":"must #include \\<windows.h> to use multi-threading with events"},{"content":"The windows.h file is required if you use multi-threading with events.","pos":[686,756]},{"content":"To fix this error, add <ph id=\"ph1\">`#include &lt;windows.h&gt;`</ph> to the top of the file in which event sources and event receivers are defined.","pos":[757,881],"source":" To fix this error, add `#include <windows.h>` to the top of the file in which event sources and event receivers are defined."}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3724 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3724\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3724\"\nms.assetid: cab8aba7-14fc-406f-8cc6-32744c8f31c1\ncaps.latest.revision: 6\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3724\nmust #include \\<windows.h> to use multi-threading with events  \n  \n The windows.h file is required if you use multi-threading with events. To fix this error, add `#include <windows.h>` to the top of the file in which event sources and event receivers are defined.  \n  \n```  \n// C3724.cpp  \n// uncomment the following line to resolve  \n// #include <windows.h>  \n  \n[event_source(native), threading(apartment)]  \nclass CEventSrc {  \npublic:  \n   __event void event1();   // C3724  \n};  \n  \n[event_receiver(native)]  \nclass CEventRec {  \npublic:  \n   void handler1() {  \n   }  \n  \n   void HookEvents(CEventSrc* pSrc) {  \n      __hook(CEventSrc::event1, pSrc, CEventRec::handler1);  \n   }  \n  \n   void UnhookEvents(CEventSrc* pSrc) {  \n      __unhook(CEventSrc::event1, pSrc, CEventRec::handler1);  \n   }  \n};  \n  \nint main() {  \n}  \n```"}